    </div> 
  </div> 

  <div class="box"> 
    <h2>🧩 Classroom Activities</h2> 
    <ul> 
      <li>🎨 Change the page background color to your favorite one</li> 
      <li>📚 Add one more book or genre to the list</li> 
      <li>🌟 Add a border around your images</li> 
      <li>🖱️ Make your link change color when the mouse moves over it</li> 
    </ul> 
  </div> 

  <div class="box"> 
    <h2>💡 Bonus Challenge</h2> 
    <p>Try adding this new section to your page:</p> 
    <pre><code>
&lt;h3&gt;🌟 Best Seller: The Story of Egypt&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Available now for only &lt;span class="price"&gt;150$&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
    </code></pre> 

    <p>And style it in CSS like this:</p> 
    <pre><code>
.price {
  color: green;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 18px;
}
    </code></pre> 
  </div> 

  <div class="box"> 
    <h2>🚀 What Students Will Achieve</h2> 
    <ul> 
      <li>✅ Create more attractive web pages</li> 
      <li>✅ Understand how links and lists work</li> 
      <li>✅ Experiment with CSS styling and colors</li> 
      <li>✅ Build confidence in HTML & CSS</li> 
    </ul> 
  </div> 

